1
00:01:25,472 --> 00:01:29,792
=Lost You Forever S2=

2
00:01:30,480 --> 00:01:32,592
=Episode 2=

3
00:01:34,346 --> 00:01:35,466
The Central Plains

4
00:01:35,865 --> 00:01:36,706
are indeed prosperous.

5
00:01:37,305 --> 00:01:39,945
No wonder His Majesty wishes
to establish the capital here.

6
00:01:41,265 --> 00:01:42,185
Being sentimental

7
00:01:43,106 --> 00:01:43,986
is a fatal for a man.

8
00:01:44,545 --> 00:01:45,505
That boy Cang Xuan

9
00:01:45,825 --> 00:01:47,945
is not as ambitious and intimidating

10
00:01:47,945 --> 00:01:49,026
as the old King of Xiyan.

11
00:01:49,786 --> 00:01:50,706
Back then...

12
00:01:56,825 --> 00:01:59,146
Xiyan braised mutton.

13
00:01:59,945 --> 00:02:02,026
Gu Shu grilled silkworms.

14
00:02:02,666 --> 00:02:04,625
There's a story
about this braised mutton.

15
00:02:04,986 --> 00:02:06,746
When the Great Emperor

16
00:02:06,746 --> 00:02:07,545
won a big victory

17
00:02:07,585 --> 00:02:08,625
in a battle,

18
00:02:09,025 --> 00:02:10,346
he rewarded the three armies.

19
00:02:10,465 --> 00:02:12,025
As it was cold,

20
00:02:12,265 --> 00:02:13,346
he stewed the mutton

21
00:02:13,506 --> 00:02:14,226
in a big pot

22
00:02:14,346 --> 00:02:15,986
and shared it with the soldiers.

23
00:02:16,545 --> 00:02:18,185
And the dish Gu Shu grilled silkworms

24
00:02:18,625 --> 00:02:21,066
was created by Queen Xiezu.

25
00:02:21,625 --> 00:02:22,346
It looks frightening,

26
00:02:22,706 --> 00:02:23,346
but it's rich

27
00:02:23,745 --> 00:02:24,586
in nutrients.

28
00:02:26,265 --> 00:02:27,346
I didn't expect

29
00:02:27,745 --> 00:02:29,625
to eat authentic Xiyan dishes
in Central Plains.

30
00:02:30,786 --> 00:02:31,786
Get the cook here,

31
00:02:31,946 --> 00:02:32,825
and I'll reward him well.

32
00:02:33,786 --> 00:02:34,448
Yes.

33
00:02:37,506 --> 00:02:38,625
It's been a long time

34
00:02:38,745 --> 00:02:40,306
since I've eaten
such authentic Xiyan food.

35
00:02:40,426 --> 00:02:41,745
If it were not for Cang Xuan,

36
00:02:42,625 --> 00:02:44,786
we would be drinking and eating at home.

37
00:02:45,665 --> 00:02:46,786
Come on. Let's drink.

38
00:02:47,185 --> 00:02:47,786
Eat.

39
00:02:48,825 --> 00:02:49,586
This tastes good.

40
00:02:49,786 --> 00:02:50,320
So authentic.

41
00:02:50,426 --> 00:02:51,786
It's the taste of Xiyan.

42
00:02:54,665 --> 00:02:55,226
Everyone.

43
00:02:56,465 --> 00:02:57,025
This is the cook

44
00:02:57,706 --> 00:03:00,025
who prepared the dishes for you.

45
00:03:00,506 --> 00:03:01,066
Please.

46
00:03:10,185 --> 00:03:12,506
- Greetings, Your Majesty.
- Greetings, Your Majesty.

47
00:03:12,506 --> 00:03:13,346
Rise.

48
00:03:18,265 --> 00:03:18,946
Please get up.

49
00:03:19,625 --> 00:03:20,226
Please rise.

50
00:03:20,385 --> 00:03:22,745
- Thank you, Your Majesty.
- Thank you, Your Majesty.

51
00:03:23,025 --> 00:03:23,786
No offense.

52
00:03:24,185 --> 00:03:24,946
I really don't know

53
00:03:25,265 --> 00:03:26,586
Your Majesty made these dishes.

54
00:03:28,665 --> 00:03:29,825
Because of me,

55
00:03:30,306 --> 00:03:31,545
all of you had to leave home

56
00:03:31,786 --> 00:03:33,786
and come all the way
to the Central Plains.

57
00:03:34,465 --> 00:03:35,745
You can't even

58
00:03:35,745 --> 00:03:36,706
eat hometown food here.

59
00:03:36,946 --> 00:03:37,825
I'm sorry about that.

60
00:03:38,866 --> 00:03:39,825
I made these dishes

61
00:03:40,786 --> 00:03:43,146
as my apology to you all.

62
00:03:44,625 --> 00:03:46,946
- Thank you, Your Majesty.
- Thank you, Your Majesty.

63
00:03:46,946 --> 00:03:48,346
I'm not an emperor today,

64
00:03:48,866 --> 00:03:49,786
but a kid.

65
00:03:50,066 --> 00:03:52,426
You're my elders.
Please make yourselves at home.

66
00:03:53,105 --> 00:03:53,786
Please sit down.

67
00:03:57,866 --> 00:03:58,706
Please.

68
00:03:59,506 --> 00:04:00,706
- Yes.
- Yes, Your Majesty.

69
00:04:05,465 --> 00:04:06,426
Mr. Huhe.

70
00:04:06,426 --> 00:04:07,706
What do you think of the dishes?

71
00:04:07,986 --> 00:04:09,545
Good.

72
00:04:09,986 --> 00:04:11,226
Especially the grilled silkworms

73
00:04:11,346 --> 00:04:12,306
taste as good

74
00:04:12,346 --> 00:04:13,946
as what Lady Xiezu cooked.

75
00:04:15,465 --> 00:04:16,306
Do you all remember?

76
00:04:16,746 --> 00:04:17,385
That year,

77
00:04:17,665 --> 00:04:19,225
we ventured deep into the enemy's camp,

78
00:04:19,586 --> 00:04:20,426
ran out of food

79
00:04:20,545 --> 00:04:21,626
and were seriously injured.

80
00:04:21,986 --> 00:04:23,945
But we survived

81
00:04:24,105 --> 00:04:25,225
on the silkworms raised

82
00:04:25,706 --> 00:04:26,426
by Lady Xiezu.

83
00:04:26,785 --> 00:04:27,505
Indeed.

84
00:04:28,466 --> 00:04:29,466
The queen was merciful.

85
00:04:29,706 --> 00:04:30,345
Back then,

86
00:04:30,626 --> 00:04:31,785
each soldier

87
00:04:31,785 --> 00:04:33,306
serving the Great Emperor

88
00:04:33,706 --> 00:04:36,105
owed Her Highness.

89
00:04:36,505 --> 00:04:37,545
- Yes, indeed.
- Yes.

90
00:04:37,945 --> 00:04:40,225
I heard a lot about you

91
00:04:40,545 --> 00:04:41,866
from my grandmother.

92
00:04:43,026 --> 00:04:44,265
In the past, Xiyan's territory

93
00:04:44,265 --> 00:04:45,385
covered the North and Xi Jiang.

94
00:04:46,626 --> 00:04:48,026
Now the territory is vast,

95
00:04:48,785 --> 00:04:50,065
stretching from Yuyuan in the west

96
00:04:50,505 --> 00:04:53,345
to the Donghai Sea,
governing most of Dahuang.

97
00:04:53,586 --> 00:04:55,626
It all thanks to

98
00:04:56,626 --> 00:04:58,065
your deeds of valor in battle.

99
00:04:58,385 --> 00:05:00,026
You insist on staying
in the Central Plains.

100
00:05:00,345 --> 00:05:01,265
I thought

101
00:05:01,906 --> 00:05:03,505
you were captivated

102
00:05:03,505 --> 00:05:04,586
by its prosperity

103
00:05:04,825 --> 00:05:07,345
and forgot the past hardships.

104
00:05:07,626 --> 00:05:08,825
I've decided to stay here

105
00:05:09,545 --> 00:05:10,986
not because I've forgotten the past.

106
00:05:11,385 --> 00:05:12,186
I'm walking

107
00:05:12,866 --> 00:05:14,466
the same path my grandparents took,

108
00:05:14,545 --> 00:05:16,866
leading the Xiyan clans

109
00:05:18,505 --> 00:05:20,105
to make Xiyan thrive

110
00:05:20,866 --> 00:05:22,785
and give people a peaceful life.

111
00:05:22,986 --> 00:05:25,306
I've never forgotten your contributions

112
00:05:25,545 --> 00:05:28,105
to the country.

113
00:05:33,466 --> 00:05:34,545
My men asked around.

114
00:05:35,026 --> 00:05:35,866
It is true.

115
00:05:48,105 --> 00:05:50,225
To please those old folks,

116
00:05:50,545 --> 00:05:52,586
(Xiyan Shiran)
Cang Xuan shamelessly cooked for them.

117
00:05:54,345 --> 00:05:55,866
He humiliated himself.

118
00:05:58,665 --> 00:06:00,065
Cang Xuan is scheming.

119
00:06:00,866 --> 00:06:02,825
He might have

120
00:06:03,146 --> 00:06:04,306
won over those old folks

121
00:06:04,306 --> 00:06:06,065
by a carrot-and-stick approach.

122
00:06:07,385 --> 00:06:07,986
Brother.

123
00:06:08,866 --> 00:06:10,906
We can no longer stay
in the Central Plains.

124
00:06:11,385 --> 00:06:12,306
Instead of enduring

125
00:06:12,545 --> 00:06:14,345
Cang Xuan's arrogance,

126
00:06:14,746 --> 00:06:15,426
why not

127
00:06:15,906 --> 00:06:17,265
fight him together?

128
00:06:18,466 --> 00:06:20,945
While the old clans still support us,

129
00:06:21,265 --> 00:06:21,866
take the chance

130
00:06:22,026 --> 00:06:23,866
to oppose the capital relocation

131
00:06:24,345 --> 00:06:25,545
and lead them back to Xiyan.

132
00:06:26,385 --> 00:06:28,626
Just let Cang Xuan stay here

133
00:06:29,105 --> 00:06:30,065
and be the king.

134
00:06:31,906 --> 00:06:32,586
Plus,

135
00:06:33,986 --> 00:06:34,945
you can take this chance

136
00:06:35,626 --> 00:06:37,186
to make yourself king

137
00:06:37,545 --> 00:06:38,706
in Xiyan Town.

138
00:06:40,466 --> 00:06:41,186
Brother.

139
00:06:41,746 --> 00:06:42,906
It's a rare opportunity.

140
00:06:43,105 --> 00:06:44,265
If Cang Xuan

141
00:06:44,345 --> 00:06:46,026
wins over the clans

142
00:06:46,105 --> 00:06:47,545
and secures his throne,

143
00:06:47,746 --> 00:06:48,586
I'm afraid

144
00:06:49,785 --> 00:06:51,426
we will have no more chances.

145
00:07:01,808 --> 00:07:02,385
Okay.

146
00:07:04,186 --> 00:07:04,746
Shiran.

147
00:07:06,746 --> 00:07:07,906
You invite the leaders

148
00:07:09,026 --> 00:07:11,945
of each clan to come
and discuss matters.

149
00:07:12,545 --> 00:07:15,626
Let's return to Xiyan Town together.

150
00:07:16,665 --> 00:07:17,168
Yes.

151
00:07:17,626 --> 00:07:18,785
When you have time,

152
00:07:20,665 --> 00:07:21,345
we'll go to Baili

153
00:07:22,505 --> 00:07:23,706
to remove the poisonous bug.

154
00:07:27,385 --> 00:07:28,026
Rest assured.

155
00:07:28,785 --> 00:07:29,785
After that,

156
00:07:30,706 --> 00:07:31,906
I will still keep my promise

157
00:07:31,906 --> 00:07:32,665
to you.

158
00:07:37,945 --> 00:07:38,545
Alright.

159
00:07:39,105 --> 00:07:39,906
When I have time.

160
00:07:46,825 --> 00:07:47,825
I'll deliver the pills to you

161
00:07:47,825 --> 00:07:48,545
every three months.

162
00:07:49,466 --> 00:07:50,385
I have to go.

163
00:07:59,706 --> 00:08:00,706
Join me for a meal.

164
00:08:09,026 --> 00:08:10,545
Sorry, but I don't have time.

165
00:08:12,225 --> 00:08:13,706
You better not

166
00:08:14,906 --> 00:08:16,345
refuse my invitation.

167
00:08:18,345 --> 00:08:19,825
But now you are Fangfeng Bei.

168
00:08:20,426 --> 00:08:21,626
So who were you

169
00:08:21,626 --> 00:08:22,345
talking to just now?

170
00:08:23,856 --> 00:08:24,496
Alright.

171
00:08:25,146 --> 00:08:26,265
General Xiang Liu.

172
00:08:29,665 --> 00:08:30,586
What kind of meat is this?

173
00:08:30,825 --> 00:08:31,440
It smells so good.

174
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:32,688
Donkey meat.

175
00:08:34,705 --> 00:08:35,465
In Dahuang,

176
00:08:35,506 --> 00:08:37,186
no one is better at cooking donkey meat

177
00:08:37,626 --> 00:08:38,905
than him.

178
00:08:40,665 --> 00:08:41,746
What a surprise.

179
00:08:43,506 --> 00:08:44,426
It's been centuries.

180
00:08:44,705 --> 00:08:46,266
You came with a friend
for the first time.

181
00:08:47,066 --> 00:08:48,266
(Mr. Lirong)
A girl, even.

182
00:08:50,986 --> 00:08:52,066
It's made especially for you.

183
00:08:52,624 --> 00:08:53,200
Try it.

184
00:08:53,705 --> 00:08:54,224
Thank you.

185
00:08:58,785 --> 00:08:59,905
A while ago,

186
00:09:00,785 --> 00:09:02,746
two more brothers left us.

187
00:09:04,145 --> 00:09:05,465
Those who followed Chi...

188
00:09:06,506 --> 00:09:08,866
Followed the general

189
00:09:09,785 --> 00:09:11,105
have almost all died.

190
00:09:11,626 --> 00:09:12,626
Every man will die

191
00:09:13,905 --> 00:09:14,826
sooner or later.

192
00:09:15,626 --> 00:09:16,946
You are right.

193
00:09:17,626 --> 00:09:18,866
Maybe one day,

194
00:09:19,066 --> 00:09:20,465
you and I will die.

195
00:09:27,866 --> 00:09:28,705
Look at you.

196
00:09:29,386 --> 00:09:30,345
When she's around you,

197
00:09:30,506 --> 00:09:32,105
you don't even dare

198
00:09:32,105 --> 00:09:32,656
to approach her.

199
00:09:32,986 --> 00:09:33,665
Now,

200
00:09:34,025 --> 00:09:34,986
she left with another man.

201
00:09:35,186 --> 00:09:36,785
And it makes you upset.

202
00:09:40,986 --> 00:09:42,826
What can I do even if I approach her?

203
00:09:56,506 --> 00:09:59,066
What a small world, Jing.

204
00:10:00,066 --> 00:10:00,665
What do you say?

205
00:10:11,306 --> 00:10:12,665
What's your name, young lady?

206
00:10:19,545 --> 00:10:20,306
Young lady.

207
00:10:20,826 --> 00:10:21,866
Fangfeng Bei

208
00:10:21,946 --> 00:10:23,506
is as bad

209
00:10:23,905 --> 00:10:24,866
as that old stallholder.

210
00:10:25,426 --> 00:10:26,345
He's not the right one.

211
00:10:27,066 --> 00:10:27,585
Why not

212
00:10:28,225 --> 00:10:28,905
be with my buddy?

213
00:10:30,665 --> 00:10:31,506
My buddy

214
00:10:31,665 --> 00:10:32,266
was set up

215
00:10:32,266 --> 00:10:33,225
by a woman

216
00:10:33,506 --> 00:10:34,465
and got her pregnant.

217
00:10:34,946 --> 00:10:35,472
However,

218
00:10:35,665 --> 00:10:36,386
that's not

219
00:10:36,386 --> 00:10:37,705
an unforgivable mistake, right?

220
00:10:39,066 --> 00:10:39,665
Lirong Chang!

221
00:10:43,186 --> 00:10:44,186
Just think about it.

222
00:10:44,626 --> 00:10:46,746
He made a mistake.

223
00:10:47,025 --> 00:10:48,506
So he won't make the same mistake

224
00:10:48,506 --> 00:10:49,386
again.

225
00:10:49,626 --> 00:10:50,986
After getting married, you'll have less

226
00:10:51,105 --> 00:10:52,066
to worry about.

227
00:10:52,905 --> 00:10:53,785
Are you done?

228
00:10:54,066 --> 00:10:55,306
No.

229
00:10:55,746 --> 00:10:56,986
Young lady.

230
00:10:58,186 --> 00:10:59,665
To be honest,

231
00:11:00,506 --> 00:11:02,145
Fangfeng Bei

232
00:11:02,266 --> 00:11:03,746
can't give you a stable life.

233
00:11:04,145 --> 00:11:05,746
Though Tushan Jing made a mistake,

234
00:11:05,905 --> 00:11:07,465
he's still better than Fangfeng Bei.

235
00:11:10,066 --> 00:11:11,105
I'm already engaged.

236
00:11:11,705 --> 00:11:12,866
He is not my fiancé.

237
00:11:13,785 --> 00:11:15,186
So, please.

238
00:11:15,866 --> 00:11:17,266
Stop belittling others.

239
00:11:21,186 --> 00:11:22,025
Engaged?

240
00:11:22,866 --> 00:11:23,408
To whom?

241
00:11:23,905 --> 00:11:25,426
Who dares to take my buddy's woman?

242
00:11:26,186 --> 00:11:27,066
Tell me his name.

243
00:11:27,345 --> 00:11:28,306
I'll talk to him right now.

244
00:11:28,465 --> 00:11:29,545
If he doesn't call it off,

245
00:11:29,785 --> 00:11:31,145
I'll break his legs.

246
00:11:31,585 --> 00:11:32,746
Chishui Fenglong.

247
00:11:33,826 --> 00:11:34,905
Go talk to him.

248
00:11:35,866 --> 00:11:36,368
Feng...

249
00:11:38,266 --> 00:11:40,826
You are Fenglong's fiancée?

250
00:11:45,746 --> 00:11:46,448
So,

251
00:11:46,826 --> 00:11:48,066
you are

252
00:11:48,746 --> 00:11:50,266
Princess of Haoling?

253
00:11:51,186 --> 00:11:52,626
King of Xiyan's sister?

254
00:11:55,585 --> 00:11:56,986
You are quite polite to him.

255
00:11:59,386 --> 00:12:00,426
What he said is true.

256
00:12:01,345 --> 00:12:02,105
I'm not a good man

257
00:12:02,105 --> 00:12:03,145
for any woman.

258
00:12:04,105 --> 00:12:04,905
You know it.

259
00:12:07,345 --> 00:12:09,306
You're the daughter of Princess General?

260
00:12:11,986 --> 00:12:12,866
And your father?

261
00:12:13,426 --> 00:12:14,585
I am the Princess of Haoling.

262
00:12:14,986 --> 00:12:16,306
So, my father is the King of Haoling.

263
00:12:36,010 --> 00:12:38,826
♪Rain keeps pouring♪

264
00:12:39,050 --> 00:12:42,410
♪Grass grows tall♪

265
00:12:42,864 --> 00:12:45,834
♪Snow covers all♪

266
00:12:46,288 --> 00:12:49,450
♪Grass grows tall♪

267
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:54,858
♪Be it sere or in its prime,
it surrounds the bones of loyal men♪

268
00:12:56,665 --> 00:12:58,186
Stop singing. You're drunk.

269
00:12:58,186 --> 00:13:01,826
♪Chenrong's men never yield♪

270
00:13:01,826 --> 00:13:02,866
Alright, you're drunk.

271
00:13:02,866 --> 00:13:03,705
I'm not drunk.

272
00:13:07,216 --> 00:13:08,905
♪Rain keeps pouring♪

273
00:13:08,905 --> 00:13:09,665
Stop it.

274
00:13:10,352 --> 00:13:14,096
♪Grass grows tall♪

275
00:13:14,096 --> 00:13:18,218
♪Snow covers all♪

276
00:13:18,218 --> 00:13:22,474
♪Grass grows tall♪

277
00:13:32,345 --> 00:13:32,986
Well,

278
00:13:33,705 --> 00:13:34,746
he can't hold his liquor.

279
00:13:35,626 --> 00:13:37,105
Yet he likes to drink.

280
00:13:37,345 --> 00:13:38,345
Once he gets drunk,

281
00:13:38,585 --> 00:13:39,986
he loves to sing random folk songs.

282
00:13:42,386 --> 00:13:42,905
Well,

283
00:13:43,066 --> 00:13:44,426
he lost one arm.

284
00:13:44,785 --> 00:13:46,345
And he's crippled.

285
00:13:47,626 --> 00:13:48,946
He's practically disabled.

286
00:13:49,986 --> 00:13:51,426
We're here for a meal.

287
00:13:51,785 --> 00:13:52,785
Once I leave this place,

288
00:13:52,946 --> 00:13:54,306
I will remember nothing.

289
00:13:56,585 --> 00:13:57,465
Are you done?

290
00:13:57,785 --> 00:13:58,705
Let's go if you are.

