00:30:02,945 --> 00:30:04,546
You have already served Hong Jiang

582
00:30:04,546 --> 00:30:05,305
for centuries.

583
00:30:06,185 --> 00:30:07,105
No matter what,

584
00:30:07,225 --> 00:30:08,026
you don't owe him now.

585
00:30:08,225 --> 00:30:09,305
Why not take this chance

586
00:30:09,305 --> 00:30:10,425
to unload this heavy burden?

587
00:30:10,626 --> 00:30:13,305
And you can live in seclusion

588
00:30:13,305 --> 00:30:14,386
or wander the world.

589
00:30:14,546 --> 00:30:16,305
Do whatever you want.

590
00:30:19,506 --> 00:30:21,266
Even if you meet someone you like,

591
00:30:22,465 --> 00:30:25,386
you can marry her, have children,
and spend your life with her.

592
00:30:25,866 --> 00:30:27,266
It's a joyful life.

593
00:30:30,345 --> 00:30:31,185
Grandpa.

594
00:30:31,305 --> 00:30:32,026
Grandpa.

595
00:30:32,185 --> 00:30:33,026
Grandpa.

596
00:30:33,506 --> 00:30:35,425
Grandpa, let me help you.

597
00:30:35,465 --> 00:30:36,624
Good kid.

598
00:30:36,624 --> 00:30:37,225
Let's go.

599
00:30:37,225 --> 00:30:38,305
I'll make you something tasty.

600
00:30:38,305 --> 00:30:40,065
Granny, I'll support you.

601
00:30:40,105 --> 00:30:41,225
Okay, let's go.

602
00:30:42,896 --> 00:30:43,824
Come on.

603
00:30:44,144 --> 00:30:45,585
(Rejuvenation Hall, Qingshui Town)

604
00:30:45,585 --> 00:30:47,185
Shall we go back to eat?

605
00:31:04,866 --> 00:31:06,065
If you have any requests,

606
00:31:06,465 --> 00:31:07,465
just let me know.

607
00:31:08,105 --> 00:31:09,626
The King of Xiyan will try
to fulfill you.

608
00:31:11,705 --> 00:31:12,225
No need.

609
00:31:17,026 --> 00:31:17,746
Go back.

610
00:31:28,746 --> 00:31:30,146
You stubborn nine-headed demon.

611
00:31:30,825 --> 00:31:31,906
What is it that you really want?

612
00:31:32,666 --> 00:31:33,585
You know what happened

613
00:31:33,585 --> 00:31:34,386
to Chi Chen.

614
00:31:34,786 --> 00:31:36,386
He staked his life
for the Central Plains.

615
00:31:36,386 --> 00:31:37,185
And now?

616
00:31:37,386 --> 00:31:38,266
No one remembers him.

617
00:31:39,105 --> 00:31:40,026
Haven't you seen

618
00:31:40,026 --> 00:31:40,945
the kind of life

619
00:31:40,945 --> 00:31:41,986
my uncle is living?

620
00:31:43,666 --> 00:31:45,185
This is a path doomed to failure.

621
00:31:46,266 --> 00:31:47,746
What are you holding on to?

622
00:32:11,225 --> 00:32:13,026
The mountains and rivers remain,

623
00:32:14,225 --> 00:32:16,786
but the old friends are gone.

624
00:32:23,984 --> 00:32:29,258
♪When my blood splatters
on your clothes♪

625
00:32:30,256 --> 00:32:34,474
♪It looks like peach blossoms♪

626
00:32:34,544 --> 00:32:41,546
♪As long as you can see me♪

627
00:32:42,096 --> 00:32:46,736
(Chi Chen)
♪Oh, yeah♪

628
00:32:46,736 --> 00:32:51,425
♪Please cut out my heart♪

629
00:32:51,425 --> 00:32:53,866
General!

630
00:32:54,128 --> 00:32:59,850
♪Let my blood flood the wilderness♪

631
00:33:13,666 --> 00:33:15,185
This is General Chi Chen's love song

632
00:33:15,305 --> 00:33:17,105
for his wife.

633
00:33:17,146 --> 00:33:18,585
Where did you hear it?

634
00:33:19,026 --> 00:33:19,546
Baili.

635
00:33:26,585 --> 00:33:28,266
Did the girl who came with you

636
00:33:29,585 --> 00:33:31,305
put the poisonous bug in you?

637
00:33:32,666 --> 00:33:33,666
Why?

638
00:33:36,305 --> 00:33:37,465
You should not see her anymore.

639
00:33:39,705 --> 00:33:40,465
Go to Baili.

640
00:33:41,705 --> 00:33:44,345
Wu King can remove it from you.

641
00:33:47,225 --> 00:33:48,906
The Baili people are eccentric.

642
00:33:49,945 --> 00:33:51,345
They don't like to deal with strangers.

643
00:33:53,225 --> 00:33:53,906
Why will the Wu King

644
00:33:53,906 --> 00:33:55,225
help a stranger?

645
00:33:55,585 --> 00:33:56,146
He will.

646
00:33:57,305 --> 00:33:58,705
As long as he sees that girl,

647
00:33:58,705 --> 00:33:59,705
he will definitely help you.

648
00:34:00,185 --> 00:34:01,386
That girl is...

649
00:34:08,385 --> 00:34:09,306
What?

650
00:34:10,465 --> 00:34:11,145
Never mind.

651
00:34:13,905 --> 00:34:15,225
Great Princess of Haoling

652
00:34:16,865 --> 00:34:17,786
and Chi Chen,

653
00:34:19,986 --> 00:34:21,266
what exactly is their relationship?

654
00:34:28,266 --> 00:34:29,826
It will not work out.

655
00:34:30,865 --> 00:34:31,945
You better let her go.

656
00:34:32,145 --> 00:34:33,586
Your positions are different.

657
00:34:34,945 --> 00:34:36,905
Don't end up like the general.

658
00:34:37,225 --> 00:34:38,385
He was in love with a woman

659
00:34:38,746 --> 00:34:40,546
but had to fight her to the death

660
00:34:40,546 --> 00:34:41,986
on the battlefield.

661
00:34:48,865 --> 00:34:49,465
You two

662
00:34:50,705 --> 00:34:51,905
have different positions.

663
00:34:52,306 --> 00:34:54,066
It's doomed to have no good outcome.

664
00:34:54,705 --> 00:34:55,905
You better stop.

665
00:34:56,465 --> 00:34:57,225
Let her go.

666
00:34:58,385 --> 00:34:59,826
Don't see her again.

667
00:35:00,546 --> 00:35:01,945
Stop it.

668
00:35:11,746 --> 00:35:12,385
Don't worry.

669
00:35:16,865 --> 00:35:17,665
She said

670
00:35:19,506 --> 00:35:20,865
I couldn't appear in her dreams.

671
00:35:42,986 --> 00:35:44,066
The person she likes

672
00:35:45,346 --> 00:35:46,066
is not me.

673
00:36:21,145 --> 00:36:21,865
Your Highness.

674
00:36:22,185 --> 00:36:23,465
The weather is nice.

675
00:36:23,905 --> 00:36:24,945
How about archery practice?

676
00:36:25,625 --> 00:36:26,266
I don't want to.

677
00:36:26,746 --> 00:36:27,826
How about making pills?

678
00:36:28,425 --> 00:36:29,586
His Majesty has sent rare herbs

679
00:36:29,586 --> 00:36:30,665
to you.

680
00:36:32,346 --> 00:36:32,945
Not interested.

681
00:36:33,586 --> 00:36:35,306
(Miao Pu, Shan Hu)
How about playing the zither?

682
00:36:35,986 --> 00:36:36,705
Snacks?

683
00:36:37,385 --> 00:36:39,225
Or have a few drinks?

684
00:36:41,425 --> 00:36:42,266
Not interested.

685
00:36:57,026 --> 00:36:57,616
Xiaoyao.

686
00:37:00,225 --> 00:37:00,826
What's wrong?

687
00:37:01,506 --> 00:37:02,905
You've been listless recently.

688
00:37:07,786 --> 00:37:08,368
Not at all.

689
00:37:08,945 --> 00:37:10,306
Everything is going well.

690
00:37:13,026 --> 00:37:14,066
How about you?

691
00:37:14,786 --> 00:37:15,385
Are you happy?

692
00:37:15,986 --> 00:37:16,506
Why?

693
00:37:17,266 --> 00:37:18,385
Why ask that all of a sudden?

694
00:37:20,586 --> 00:37:21,945
Miao Pu said

695
00:37:22,665 --> 00:37:24,705
you always sat late into the night.

696
00:37:25,066 --> 00:37:26,266
I thought you would get better

697
00:37:26,266 --> 00:37:27,145
after a while.

698
00:37:27,625 --> 00:37:29,465
But you seem more and more upset.

699
00:37:30,546 --> 00:37:31,546
I'm very worried about you.

700
00:37:33,266 --> 00:37:34,826
Maybe it's because you're the King now,

701
00:37:34,905 --> 00:37:36,066
and I have no pressure.

702
00:37:36,705 --> 00:37:38,145
So my life

703
00:37:38,586 --> 00:37:39,986
is not as disciplined as before.

704
00:37:42,746 --> 00:37:43,705
Is that really so?

705
00:37:45,746 --> 00:37:47,026
Don't look at me like that.

706
00:37:51,705 --> 00:37:53,306
I thought that once I was enthroned,

707
00:37:55,026 --> 00:37:55,865
I could give you

708
00:37:55,865 --> 00:37:57,145
what I couldn't before

709
00:37:58,266 --> 00:37:59,786
and make your life better than before.

710
00:38:01,145 --> 00:38:02,546
But you are not happy now.

711
00:38:03,905 --> 00:38:05,546
Did I do something wrong?

712
00:38:08,625 --> 00:38:09,986
It's not your fault.

713
00:38:13,066 --> 00:38:14,346
It's my problem.

714
00:38:14,986 --> 00:38:15,945
You tell me

715
00:38:17,746 --> 00:38:18,746
what goes wrong.

716
00:38:20,786 --> 00:38:22,185
Recently,

717
00:38:23,786 --> 00:38:26,106
I've been thinking about Qingshui Town

718
00:38:27,225 --> 00:38:28,665
and the days

719
00:38:29,506 --> 00:38:31,066
we spent in the Zhaoyun Hall.

720
00:38:32,225 --> 00:38:33,905
I cherish those good times.

721
00:38:35,306 --> 00:38:36,625
But I don't like indulging

722
00:38:36,826 --> 00:38:38,385
in the past.

723
00:38:39,306 --> 00:38:40,705
Even if the past was beautiful,

724
00:38:41,665 --> 00:38:42,905
I have to move on.

725
00:38:43,786 --> 00:38:44,945
The past is the past.

726
00:38:46,106 --> 00:38:47,705
But I don't know what's wrong with me.

727
00:38:49,225 --> 00:38:50,066
I just

728
00:38:52,506 --> 00:38:54,905
always think of Shiqi.

729
00:38:57,346 --> 00:38:58,425
I don't know

730
00:38:58,425 --> 00:38:59,746
why I am so weak.

731
00:39:02,026 --> 00:39:03,665
I don't like who I am now.

732
00:39:06,266 --> 00:39:06,945
Xiaoyao.

733
00:39:09,746 --> 00:39:11,546
You are not alone now.

734
00:39:13,465 --> 00:39:15,306
I'm here for you. You can cry.

735
00:39:15,945 --> 00:39:16,786
You can be weak.

736
00:39:17,746 --> 00:39:18,346
It's okay.

737
00:39:20,705 --> 00:39:21,865
In the past,

738
00:39:22,945 --> 00:39:23,865
if I became weak

739
00:39:25,266 --> 00:39:26,826
when facing something,

740
00:39:27,346 --> 00:39:28,346
I would die.

741
00:39:29,546 --> 00:39:30,786
So, I told myself

742
00:39:30,826 --> 00:39:32,026
I couldn't be weak.

743
00:39:34,346 --> 00:39:35,786
I just don't understand.

744
00:39:37,346 --> 00:39:38,625
I've gone through so much pain

745
00:39:38,705 --> 00:39:39,625
before.

746
00:39:41,185 --> 00:39:42,306
Why do I

747
00:39:43,905 --> 00:39:45,425
feel so heartbroken now?

748
00:39:46,945 --> 00:39:48,465
Just a man, right?

749
00:39:58,306 --> 00:39:59,225
Why do you

750
00:39:59,266 --> 00:40:00,266
look even more upset than me?

751
00:40:01,986 --> 00:40:02,746
Don't worry.

752
00:40:03,385 --> 00:40:05,185
Time heals all wounds.

753
00:40:11,346 --> 00:40:12,945
Many years ago, I knew

754
00:40:14,865 --> 00:40:17,026
that emotional wounds are hard to heal.

755
00:40:19,425 --> 00:40:20,986
So, many years later,

756
00:40:21,026 --> 00:40:21,905
I can't forgive my mother

757
00:40:21,905 --> 00:40:23,586
for killing herself before my eyes.

758
00:40:25,385 --> 00:40:26,705
No matter how much I cried and begged,

759
00:40:28,586 --> 00:40:29,905
she still left me.

760
00:40:33,145 --> 00:40:34,905
Physical wounds can heal.

761
00:40:35,865 --> 00:40:36,586
I believe

762
00:40:37,225 --> 00:40:39,306
there must be a way
to heal emotional wounds as well.

763
00:40:40,986 --> 00:40:41,945
I believe it too.

764
00:40:44,425 --> 00:40:46,145
It's just I can't forgive my mother.

765
00:40:48,066 --> 00:40:49,506
But now, with your companionship,

766
00:40:50,385 --> 00:40:51,945
the pain of losing her

767
00:40:52,586 --> 00:40:53,865
has long gone.

768
00:40:54,865 --> 00:40:55,986
The happiness now

769
00:40:56,786 --> 00:40:58,586
can heal past wounds.

770
00:40:59,786 --> 00:41:01,425
Are you encouraging me

771
00:41:01,786 --> 00:41:03,705
to start a new relationship?

772
00:41:08,106 --> 00:41:09,905
I hope someone

773
00:41:11,306 --> 00:41:11,986
can heal the pain

774
00:41:11,986 --> 00:41:13,986
Tushan Jing caused you.

775
00:41:15,786 --> 00:41:17,066
And someone else will make you

776
00:41:17,905 --> 00:41:18,705
feel valued,

777
00:41:19,546 --> 00:41:20,425
cherished,

778
00:41:21,106 --> 00:41:21,945
and adored.

779
00:41:23,106 --> 00:41:24,346
And no matter what,

780
00:41:24,905 --> 00:41:26,266
he will never abandon you.

781
00:41:30,546 --> 00:41:31,465
Well,

782
00:41:31,986 --> 00:41:34,266
I've been unlucky since childhood.

783
00:41:34,945 --> 00:41:36,346
I don't think

784
00:41:37,425 --> 00:41:38,705
I'll meet someone like that.

785
00:41:39,696 --> 00:41:40,306
You will.

786
00:41:49,145 --> 00:41:49,746
Xiaoyao.

787
00:41:52,385 --> 00:41:52,944
You will.

788
00:42:00,705 --> 00:42:02,225
(If I had known)

789
00:42:03,106 --> 00:42:03,945
(you would cry)

790
00:42:03,945 --> 00:42:06,066
(over Tushan Jing,)

791
00:42:06,986 --> 00:42:08,026
(even if I wanted the help)

792
00:42:08,026 --> 00:42:09,465
(of the Tushan Family,)

793
00:42:09,665 --> 00:42:12,145
(I couldn't have given him the chance
to get close to you.)

794
00:42:14,145 --> 00:42:16,266
(Now I hate Tushan Jing.)

795
00:42:17,465 --> 00:42:19,746
(But I hate myself even more.)

796
00:42:43,338 --> 00:42:47,280
(Tushan)

797
00:43:19,098 --> 00:43:22,330
♪Looking back on my old days♪

798
00:43:23,616 --> 00:43:27,898
♪I was unruffled
with no sorrow and soreness♪

799
00:43:29,978 --> 00:43:34,778
♪In my chaotic life,
I failed to meet your gaze♪

800
00:43:37,914 --> 00:43:40,186
♪Only emptiness remained♪

801
00:43:43,130 --> 00:43:46,202
♪Enduring all things in my life♪

802
00:43:48,051 --> 00:43:52,442
♪I valued all but indifferent
to wealth and fame♪

803
00:43:53,978 --> 00:43:59,451
♪Basking in the sun,
I couldn't feel your sunlight♪

804
00:44:00,402 --> 00:44:06,234
♪All I feel is a painful heat wave♪

805
00:44:09,082 --> 00:44:13,818
♪All things are dim,
while only your eyes shine bright♪

806
00:44:15,130 --> 00:44:19,642
♪I'll follow my heart
and go to chase the sun far away♪

807
00:44:21,082 --> 00:44:27,034
♪Everything seems sad,
while only your brows raise in delight♪

808
00:44:27,811 --> 00:44:32,122
♪I'm waiting for you
to enjoy the scenery at night♪

809
00:44:33,114 --> 00:44:38,080
♪You came with wind and rain,
while left with my four seasons♪

810
00:44:39,072 --> 00:44:43,680
♪All is bleak without you♪

811
00:44:45,018 --> 00:44:50,624
♪It began like a tornado,
and went away leaving only dust♪

812
00:44:51,738 --> 00:45:02,752
♪Without you,
even the most beautiful world is a mess♪
